2026-05-12T03:11:53.4790187Z 22    <!--
2026-05-12T03:11:53.4790685Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-12T03:11:53.4791319Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-12T03:11:53.4791941Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-12T03:11:53.4792687Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-12T03:11:53.4812616Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-12T03:11:53.4813642Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-12T03:11:53.4814368Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-12T03:11:53.4815114Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-12T03:11:53.4815867Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-12T03:11:53.4816571Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
