2026-05-12T03:11:53.9311277Z 25            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-12T03:11:53.9311598Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-12T03:11:53.9311919Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-12T03:11:53.9312239Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-12T03:11:53.9312571Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-12T03:11:53.9312887Z 30        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-12T03:11:53.9313162Z 31        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
